    avcodec/vorbis: 1 << 31 > int32_t::max(), so use 1u << 31 instead.
    
    Signed-off-by: Dale Curtis <dalecurtis@chromium.org>
    Signed-off-by: Michael Niedermayer <michael@niedermayer.cc>

